pedia.org/resource/Matteo_Salvini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matteo_Salvini\"}, {\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.7355182715831872, \"rank\": 0.2879490902489719, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"a really bad start\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We imagined a ceremony to show our values and our principles so we gave a very committed message,\\\" Paris 2024 president Tony Estanguet said.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.47907368658919e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ceremony\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"our values\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"our principles\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"a very committed message\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea was to really trigger a reflection.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"a reflection\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to have a message as strong as possible.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Naturally, we had to take into account the international community.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"account\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"the international community\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having said that - it is a French ceremony for the French Games - so we trusted our artistic director.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9886250708315673, \"rank\": 0.008598897181296432, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the French Games\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"our artistic director\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have freedom of expression in France and we wanted to protect it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9990258042806759, \"rank\": 0.0009196516470488439, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"expression\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps told a press conference: \\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.47907368658919e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(The opening ceremony) tried to celebrate community tolerance.\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offence, we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"any offence\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 artistic director Thomas Jolly was left baffled by the negative reactions to the show and said the scene had not been inspired byThe Last Supperand depicted a pagan feast linked to the gods of Olympus in order to celebrate diversity and pay tribute to feasting and French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 2310, \